# Word_Counter
Simple Flask Word Counter


Please make sure to install **python** & **requirements** before using the program:

```
pip install -r requirements.txt

```
###to run the program:

```
cd ~/Word_Counter 
source env/bin/activate
python app.py

```

The go to [http://localhost:5000/](http://localhost:5000/)

###To to

Before starting please check out [git flow branching model](http://nvie.com/files/Git-branching-model.pdf)
